  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel offers a half board basis which includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>Full Continental buffet breakfast for 7 mornings with hot options provided on 6 mornings per week</li>
<li>Afternoon tea and coffee with cake and savoury treats on 6 days, including soup, sandwiches and scones</li>
<li>3 course evening evening meals with set menu served 6 days, including pre-dinner glass of prosecco with canapés, a choice of complimentary wine &amp; tea/coffee</li>
<li><span>Complimentary tea &amp; coffee available throughout the day</span></li>
<li>Special celebration menus on Christmas Day &amp; New Year's Eve<span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span>(Breakfast hot options, afternoon tea &amp; dinner is 6 days per week due to Hotel staff's day off)</span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
