  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Ducs de Savoie is a family-friendly hotel in the centre of Val d'Isere just a few minutes' walk to the main ski lifts and slopes.  Offering a cosy bar area, 36 nicely furnished rooms and tasty evening meals on half board <span>including breakfast, afternoon tea and evening meals with wine.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Save £100pp when you pre-book your ski pass and lift hire/carriage.</strong></span></p>]]></listingDescription>
