  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>We offer a choice of comfortable bedrooms for friends and couples as well as some larger rooms so all family sizes can be catered for. Some bedrooms have a shared hallway with an additional door to the corridor, which is ideal for families.</p>
<p>All bedrooms have been updated with new carpets, headboards, lights and Nespresso coffee machines. You can chose and book your own room number from the list of rooms below.</p>
<p>Many bedrooms have a third bed similar to a top bunk or cabin bed, with a wardrobe beneath, and is situated in the entrance hallway of the room (suitable for children over six years old). A fourth put-up-bed for children can be added in many rooms.</p>
<p><strong>First Floor</strong></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 101*</span> - Double or Twin beds, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 102*</span> - Double bed, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 103*</span> - Double or Twin beds, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 104*</span> - Double bed, bath, WC and balcony </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 105</span> - Double or Twin beds, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 106*</span> - Double or twin beds, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 107*</span> - Double or Twin beds, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Suite 11</span> - Double bedroom with balcony and separate lounge area with 2 single sofa beds, balcony and single bed in alcove near entrance, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 12</span> - Twin beds and single bed in alcove near entrance, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 14</span> - Twin beds and two single beds in alcove area near entrance, shower and WC</p>
<p>Rooms 12 &amp; 14 combine to make a larger suite sleeping 6-7, as both rooms lead off from a private corridor with door</p>
<p>* Rooms 101, 102, 103, 104, 106 and 107 have a third bed similar to a single top bunk suitable for children only. </p>
<p>Most rooms on the first floor have twin or double beds so please let us know your preference if booking on of these.</p>
<p><strong>Second Floor</strong></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 201*</span> - Twin beds, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 202*</span> - Double bed, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 203*</span> - Twin beds, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 204*</span> - Double bed, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 205</span> - Double bed, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 206*</span> - Double, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 207*</span> - Twin beds, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 208*</span> - Twin, bath and WC (shares a hallway with room 209)</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 209</span> - Double, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Suite 21</span> - Double bed, sofa bed in lounge, single bed in alcove, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 22</span> - Twin beds, additional single bed in alcove, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 23</span> - Twin beds, additional single bed in alcove, shower and WC</p>
<p>* Rooms 201, 202, 203, 204, 206, 207 and 208 have a third bed similar to a single top bunk, suitable for children only. </p>
<p><strong>Third Floor</strong></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 301*</span> - Twin beds, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 302*</span> - Double bed, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 303*</span> - Double bed, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 304*</span> - Twin beds plus a double bed on mezzanine level, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 307*</span> - Twin beds, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 308*</span> - Twin beds, bath and WC (shares a hallway with room 309)</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 309</span> - Double bed, bath and WC</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Suite 31</span> - Double bedroom, separate lounge area with twin sofa bed, mezzanine with a single bed and put-up bed, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p>* Rooms 301, 302, 303, 304, 307 and 308 have a third bed similar to a single top bunk, suitable for children only. </p>
<p><strong>Fourth Floor</strong></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 401*</span> - Twin beds, bath, WC and balcony</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Room 402*</span> - Double bed, bath, WC and balcony</p>
